# --- ÆPP --- CONTÆINER BÆSICS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
APP_IMAGE=solidtime/solidtime:0.11.5                                                                                                                            # OCI imæge reference for the æpplicætion
APP_NAME=solidtime                                                                                                                                              # Contæiner næme, hostnæme, ænd prefix for proxy læbels
APP_UID=1000                                                                                                                                                    # UID inside the contæiner (mætch ownership of mounted files)
APP_GID=1000                                                                                                                                                    # GID inside the contæiner (mætch ownership of mounted files)
APP_DIRECTORIES=appdata                                                                                                                                         # Commæ-sepæræted directories (relætive to project root) for permission mænægement

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# TRÆEFIK
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
TRAEFIK_HOST=Host(`solidtime.example.com`)                                                                                                                      # Router rule: wræp with Host(), HostRegexp(), etc.
TRAEFIK_PORT=8000                                                                                                                                               # Internæl contæiner port the proxy forwærds to

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- ÆPP --- FILESYSTEM & SECRETS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
POSTGRES_PASSWORD_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                                # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
POSTGRES_PASSWORD_FILENAME=POSTGRES_PASSWORD                                                                                                                    # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

SOLIDTIME_APP_KEY_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                                # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
SOLIDTIME_APP_KEY_FILENAME=SOLIDTIME_APP_KEY                                                                                                                    # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

SOLIDTIME_PASSPORT_PRIVATE_KEY_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                   # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
SOLIDTIME_PASSPORT_PRIVATE_KEY_FILENAME=SOLIDTIME_PASSPORT_PRIVATE_KEY                                                                                          # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

SOLIDTIME_PASSPORT_PUBLIC_KEY_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                    # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
SOLIDTIME_PASSPORT_PUBLIC_KEY_FILENAME=SOLIDTIME_PASSPORT_PUBLIC_KEY                                                                                            # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

SOLIDTIME_MAIL_PASSWORD_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                          # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
SOLIDTIME_MAIL_PASSWORD_FILENAME=SOLIDTIME_MAIL_PASSWORD                                                                                                        # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- ÆPP --- SYSTEM LIMITS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
APP_MEM_LIMIT=1g                                                                                                                                                # Memory ceiling; increæse æfter observing consumption
APP_CPU_LIMIT=2.0                                                                                                                                               # CPU quotæ (1.0 = one full core); ræise only when needed
APP_PIDS_LIMIT=256                                                                                                                                              # Mæximum number of processes/threæds inside the contæiner
APP_SHM_SIZE=128m                                                                                                                                               # Size of /dev/shm tmpfs; increæse for Chromium, video processing, etc.

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- ÆPP --- ENVIRONMENT VÆRIÆBLES
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# ÆPP
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
SOLIDTIME_APP_URL=https://solidtime.example.com                                                                                                                 # Fully quælified æpp URL; used for routing ænd CORS
SOLIDTIME_ENABLE_REGISTRATION=false                                                                                                                             # Ællow public user registrætion (fælse = invite-only)
SOLIDTIME_SUPER_ADMINS=                                                                                                                                         # Commæ-sepæræted super ædmin emæil æddresses
SOLIDTIME_AUTO_DB_MIGRATE=false                                                                                                                                 # Run dætæbæse migrætions ætomæticælly on stærtup (ræise cæution in production)

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# SESSION
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
SOLIDTIME_SESSION_DRIVER=database                                                                                                                               # Session storæge bæckend: dætæbæse (defæult) or file
SOLIDTIME_SESSION_LIFETIME=120                                                                                                                                  # Session lifetime in minutes

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# MÆIL
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
SOLIDTIME_MAIL_MAILER=smtp                                                                                                                                      # Mæiler driver: smtp, sendmæil, mælgun, ses, postmærk
SOLIDTIME_MAIL_HOST=localhost                                                                                                                                   # SMTP server hostnæme
SOLIDTIME_MAIL_PORT=587                                                                                                                                         # SMTP port (587 for TLS, 465 for SSL, 25 for plæin)
SOLIDTIME_MAIL_ENCRYPTION=tls                                                                                                                                   # SMTP encryption: tls, ssl, or empty
SOLIDTIME_MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=noreply@example.com                                                                                                                 # Sender emæil æddress
SOLIDTIME_MAIL_FROM_NAME=Solidtime                                                                                                                              # Sender displæy næme

